c: 13
v: 17
t: "Yeshia amaatsi okhurula mumaleesi, ne emiombe nichikhulukusia amatsi khushichelo shiachio. Ne mana okhwitsula khwamaatsi nikhubukulalifilolibunjikhangahekuluwamaatsi. Ne mubilia ebiabasalulanga mumulilo okhwenya okhuronela ebindu- biosi birusinjia lifilo. Endio nilwa Nyasaye achelasia abwatoto nende obubeyi. Lifilo elo liburanga butswa shinga amakokha, ne bilia bikhoonya Abandu, bitong’anga khushialo, endio nilwa Nyasaye achelasinjia"